## Live field metadata (PROD `.env` tokens)

Prefer real API names over guessing:

```bash
pnpm meta:fetch -- crm <ModuleApiName>     # GET /settings/fields?module=
pnpm meta:fetch -- desk <module>           # GET /organizationFields?module=
pnpm meta:zoho-crm                         # full org catalog
pnpm meta:zoho-desk
```

CRM returns `api_name` + `data_type` (+ `json_type`). Desk returns `apiName` + `type`.

## Auth wiring

- `wrapper.authHeaders('zoho_crm'|'zoho_desk')` + `zoho.baseUrl(...)` in `src/integrations/`
- CRM: `ZOHO_CRM_API_DOMAIN` (default `…/crm/v8`), prod `ZOHO_CRM_REFRESH_TOKEN`
- Desk: `ZOHO_DESK_BASE_URL` + mandatory `orgId` (`ZOHO_DESK_ORG_ID`)

## COQL (priority for CRM reads)

`POST /coql` with `{ "select_query": "…" }`. Scope `ZohoCRM.coql.READ` + module READ.

| Limit | Max (v8 Overview) |
| --- | --- |
| SELECT fields | 500 |
| WHERE criteria | 25 |
| LIMIT per call | 2000 (default 200) |
| Same-criteria pagination | 100,000 |

Use Field Metadata / `meta:fetch` for SELECT/WHERE column API names. Max 2 lookup joins (dot notation). Beyond 100k → Bulk Read.

## Desk gotchas

Update = **PATCH**; delete = **POST …/moveToTrash**; empty list = **HTTP 204**; IDs are **strings**; `departmentId` required on ticket/task/call/event lists.
